Package: RBOINC.cl
Title: This Package Allow you to Run your Tasks at BOINC Server. Current Status: Beta-4
Version: 0.9.4.207
URL: https://r-forge.r-project.org/R/?group_id=540
BugReports: https://r-forge.r-project.org/tracker/?group_id=540
