Description: Running tasks on a BOINC server. This software consist of 3 parts. 
  The server part must be installed at BOINC server before using this package. 
  You must also build your custom virtual machine with R and install vm part at
  this machine (pre-built VMs can be found here:
  <https://disk.yandex.ru/d/e_aItFuMPfKF2A>). Virtual machine is a part of BOINC
  application, therefore you must download it to your BOINC server.
Imports: R.utils, askpass, foreach, httr, ssh, xml2, stats, utils, doParallel, parallel
